Usage
=====

    git clone git://github.com/kylef/nginx-config.git /var/nginx/conf

Adding a new site
=================

To add a new site please see the examples/ to find what base configuration you want to use. Then copy the example to sites-enabled and edit the example to suit your needs.

    cp examples/<example>.conf sites-enabled/site.conf
    vim sites-enabled/site.conf

